{"tid":1036003,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"剃鬚成日整損搞到生瘡","createTime":"2019-02-25T02:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T15:40:33.000Z","uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"86a91c6675b441b201b815ab931ab41fe7bf1aa6","tid":1036003,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"以前用剃刀成日整親<br />\n諗住轉用電鬚刨以為會好少少，點知都會整損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家下巴生左兩粒瘡，好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a3855cc2a647844ff42bf4899c0bd68d7b569f7","tid":1036003,"uid":30468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"要用鬚後水或鬚後啫喱"},{"pid":"1eea56cdb87a57fb81ba804ace5ef501fc60cb02","tid":1036003,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:31:21.000Z","msg":"有冇用剃鬚膏?用左都係咁 ?"},{"pid":"a24a2b427bcc75410d86e0c8aa21b9598424f2b9","tid":1036003,"uid":66260,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:33:07.000Z","msg":"原來電鬚刨都要用剃鬚膏同鬚後水?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17f3a7dd68ecc049554e104b9549dd3bced19f38","tid":1036003,"uid":167737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"冇整損但成撚日剃完都會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2987bfe0e083d179f7166cf978ae82f8bd77e8c4","tid":1036003,"uid":159306,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:36:14.000Z","msg":"試下用下唔同牌子鬚刨"},{"pid":"769ba3823a5776bbfe01cc3fe1f7c268bc8f7266","tid":1036003,"uid":30468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17f3a7dd68ecc049554e104b9549dd3bced19f38","tid":1036003,"uid":167737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:34:39.000Z","msg":"冇整損但成撚日剃完都會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"你以為冇剃損<br />\n其實都會有少少傷口<br />\n鬚後做啲保養會好好多"},{"pid":"756268f467c30e86772232dccdaba39d3047342d","tid":1036003,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:37:40.000Z","msg":"1.順住剃,唔好逆剃<br />\n2.鬚後水或鬚後啫喱<br />\n3.清潔多D鬚刨<br />\n4.剃前後洗面"},{"pid":"b073b96b12ebc5c1ab123c446bededb18934b9be","tid":1036003,"uid":100623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:39:48.000Z","msg":"有無d鬚刨清潔消毒野賣？<br />\n我淨係用水沖好似唔夠乾淨"},{"pid":"c68d85f213da641690c61e5735bb5801180f0ba9","tid":1036003,"uid":52283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:41:09.000Z","msg":"金屬刀片很容易滋生細菌，加上刀片刮走了表皮層，呢點是大多數剃鬍後紅腫生瘡的原因，<br />\n完成剃鬍鬚後塗抹一些鬚後水作為消毒應該可以解決"},{"pid":"f4cbb3131fefd32c8359430b92d0ebdf364531ef","tid":1036003,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:42:22.000Z","msg":"買茶樹油 剃完so就用"},{"pid":"d6d95cb807a412d61bbc021cbc09fdba88ba2233","tid":1036003,"uid":165404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a91c6675b441b201b815ab931ab41fe7bf1aa6","tid":1036003,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"以前用剃刀成日整親<br />\n諗住轉用電鬚刨以為會好少少，點知都會整損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家下巴生左兩粒瘡，好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:44:16.000Z","msg":"我都係，成個下巴有幾粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ec931f7fc93d4bcf45864f13380106911434df","tid":1036003,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:44:25.000Z","msg":"試過用鬚後水，嘴邊皮膚紅曬，迫住要戴口罩返工"},{"pid":"f152f204808e41e8b456205720bb324a9eef8a5a","tid":1036003,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:45:56.000Z","msg":"你用邊隻電動鬚刨？等我認住唔買<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除刀網爛咗，未試過刮損"},{"pid":"d8fd1a6ccfc1b87abcc82395319f5ecf90a5433d","tid":1036003,"uid":11719,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:49:17.000Z","msg":"我用百靈牌，刀頭係淘寶(平好狠多)，乜都唔搽用左幾年都無事"},{"pid":"815d5973c2919dab3d8a015f507cb58ac92cbf59","tid":1036003,"uid":40297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:49:30.000Z","msg":"個人覺得幾時剃都好緊要，盡量沖完熱水涼後，或者訓醒覺（要用熱毛巾）<br />\n第一次順剃，盡量慢慢一下落唔好翻手剃同一位置, 剃哂用暖水沖一沖，再重複落少量鬚膏剃多次。如果要逆剃一定要好輕手同埋係第兩部先可以逆。<br />\n最後用凍水洗面，鬚後水呢d可以用 因為都有消毒作用<br />\n同埋鬚刀要放係通風位置，用前我習慣性用熱水沖沖先"},{"pid":"a359d529905674a6f3b74e3013ad8eba83e8c5dc","tid":1036003,"uid":40297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57ec931f7fc93d4bcf45864f13380106911434df","tid":1036003,"uid":112416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:44:25.000Z","msg":"試過用鬚後水，嘴邊皮膚紅曬，迫住要戴口罩返工"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:51:24.000Z","msg":"有d人係會敏感，我會用鵝羅納英軟膏"},{"pid":"1b3fda173ec4880ddbed8c246e68b6550b3e4dd1","tid":1036003,"uid":132106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:53:18.000Z","msg":"拔啦 試完返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a606b6bff8ceae5679021952a7a6b0dd11d2ad43","tid":1036003,"uid":240228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86a91c6675b441b201b815ab931ab41fe7bf1aa6","tid":1036003,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-25T02:27:11.000Z","msg":"以前用剃刀成日整親<br />\n諗住轉用電鬚刨以為會好少少，點知都會整損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家下巴生左兩粒瘡，好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T15:40:33.000Z","msg":"剃鬚膏都唔識用死撚左去啦"}]}